{"tid":1113524,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個大中華膠老豆 可以點駁嘴","createTime":"2019-04-18T03:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T23:01:27.000Z","uid":175039,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"04c623d51e3c518139a5dcf88eb9dc9751a8670c","tid":1113524,"uid":175039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:03:57.000Z","msg":"我老豆好中意睇抗日神劇 同韓國瑜d濕鳩新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有日食飯佢又韓國瑜 我忍唔住屌鳩d節目賣台<br />\n跟住佢又係果三督屁<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:台灣敢宣傳獨立 大陸一定打鳩台灣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:你流緊中國人既血 你就係中國人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:中國咁多人 得中共先有辦法管得住<br />\n<br />\n點先可以屌柒我個on9老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a2af712d11b2e88f8e1aa8f7af6bff3305c931","tid":1113524,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:07:30.000Z","msg":"有次我喺巴士咁講<br />\n<br />\n你支持林鄭又要反居民反領展加租有咩好嘈？你立法會投俾邊個？你呢啲叫自己攞黎"},{"pid":"554f0dcd7a9aadca4dd1c6fcec5971490d362a88","tid":1113524,"uid":189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:08:18.000Z","msg":"呢啲係大中華膠？"},{"pid":"4214dde535296ba0e429419de06959cf20c43ebc","tid":1113524,"uid":245016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一直想知喺乜環境下成長會令一個人真係相信共產黨。"},{"pid":"c349cf1ab136c1d3275694f669f389a060cd70d5","tid":1113524,"uid":225760,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:17:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe872a42c68deca5a78d7f89d1ac88c5216a4a38","tid":1113524,"uid":175039,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c349cf1ab136c1d3275694f669f389a060cd70d5","tid":1113524,"uid":225760,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2